products.title: Hive Silkweave Elephant Pleated Skylight Blind
products.description: This textured fabric features a stripe within its pattern. Hive silkweave would look in place in a kitchen or conservatory with added green plants to add to the bohemian feel. This fabric features a honey-combed structure, meaning the guide wires are hidden from view. Product id: db-pls0118 fabric colour: elephant material: 100% polyester headrail: white rails and hardware with pull down tab and visible guide wires to support the blind fabric.
